high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter then turn left to face the green garbage.
Pick up the sponge  that's in the green garbage.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Put the sponge in the bowl that's to the right of the wine bottle.
Pick up the bowl with the sponge in it.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the shelves.
Put the bowl on the middle shelf all the way to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a sponge in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the green bin on the floor, against the stove.
Pick up the green sponge, inside the green bin on the floor.
Turn to the island on your right.
Place the sponge in the bowl, between the plate and the spoon, on the island.
Pick up the bowl, with the sponge inside it, from the kitchen island.
Turn to your right and go to the wooden shelf in front of you.
Place the bowl with the sponge inside it on the right side of the second shelf up, from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl containing a sponge on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the green trash can on the floor at the end of the counter.
Take out the green sponge from the inside of the trash can.
Turn around and go to the island in the middle of the kitchen.
Place the green sponge inside the round glass bowl behind the spoon.
Pick up the bowl with the sponge in it.
Turn right and go to the shelf in the right corner across the kitchen.
Place the bowl with the sponge on the second shelf  from the bottom.
anns.task_desc: Move the bowl with the green sponge to the shelf.
